prompt.prompt_text: Provide an overview of branch distribution across municipalities. List each municipality along with the number of branches operating there.

results.sql:
SELECT ob.nazev AS municipality, COUNT(ab.id) AS branch_count
FROM all_branches_1 ab
JOIN zsj_dwh_1 zsj ON ab.kod_zsj_d = zsj.kod_zsj
JOIN obec_dwh_1 ob ON zsj.kod_obec = ob.kod_obec
GROUP BY ob.nazev
ORDER BY branch_count DESC;
